    "description": "Magic the Wandering is a Lemmings inspired roguelite puzzle platformer about helping lost wizards find a way through different dimensions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/b0a3abba4323adfc35e489354e9a1ace.poster.avif?t=1727107198\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/b0a3abba4323adfc35e489354e9a1ace.webm?t=1727107198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/b0a3abba4323adfc35e489354e9a1ace.mp4?t=1727107198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Learn spells and unlock wizard types as you progress through and try to beat the highest score and level reached. Uncover secret achievements to get some of the more powerful unlocks to help you on your next run or power up your current progress.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/86e67d9788c4ef6c80fe3d06105bda4a.poster.avif?t=1727107198\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/86e67d9788c4ef6c80fe3d06105bda4a.webm?t=1727107198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/86e67d9788c4ef6c80fe3d06105bda4a.mp4?t=1727107198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The true Lemmings successor.<br>Every stage has multiple ways of getting to the end and overcome all the obstacles.<br>Normal mode with more wizards to start with. Challenge yourself with the Highlander mode where you only have one wizard the whole run.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/c74dd0359feea3288cd8ad9a8a18a910.poster.avif?t=1727107198\" width=128 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/c74dd0359feea3288cd8ad9a8a18a910.webm?t=1727107198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/af32041af4556a54a0e54d5d098d5682.apng?t=1727107198\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/af32041af4556a54a0e54d5d098d5682.poster.avif?t=1727107198\" class=\"bb_img\" width=128 height=128 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/c57e61dad65f753a5906b544d6a6f791.apng?t=1727107198\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/c57e61dad65f753a5906b544d6a6f791.poster.avif?t=1727107198\" class=\"bb_img\" width=128 height=128 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/f70fe4948f68577440f14f8491cc7bef.apng?t=1727107198\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/f70fe4948f68577440f14f8491cc7bef.poster.avif?t=1727107198\" class=\"bb_img\" width=128 height=128 /></picture></span><br><br>Use different wizard types with their own special abilities.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> learn spells for all wizards to use<br></li><li> modifiers for spells to alter their effects<br></li><li> find and unlock different wizard types useable for subsequent runs<br></li><li> progressive difficulty increase per each level<br></li><li> environment specific hazards and enemies<br></li><li> try to rank up in a global leaderboard</li></ul><br>Relive the nostalgia of a Lemmings game with a modern take on it. Prepare your party and venture toward the unknown. These guys are truly lost.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/42bfec63783f51d419bcce22e6586257.poster.avif?t=1727107198\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/42bfec63783f51d419bcce22e6586257.webm?t=1727107198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Hand-crafter pixel art visuals and chiptunes music done by a solo dev.",
